        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "The release of ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Pokémon Legends: Arceus",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " is an exciting time for the series. As the largest multimedia franchise in the world, to see the series stray away from its usual formula and the many remakes comes as a breath of fresh air. ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Legends: Arceus",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " takes place in the feudal Japanese-inspired region of Hisui, in a time where the modern and futuristic technology seen in the traditional games haven’t been invented yet. There is no Pokédex yet and Poké Balls have only just been invented. Having traveled back in time, the player is asked to help write the first Pokédex. At a simple glance, one familiar with Pokémon can see the differences immediately and clearly and yet, one might wonder whether there is too much of a difference at all.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "type": "embed",
        "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=I4RynqpahT8",
        "html": "<iframe width=\"200\" height=\"113\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/I4RynqpahT8?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe>",
        "metadata": {
          "title": "Pokémon Legends: Arceus - Overview Trailer - Nintendo Switch",
          "author_name": "Nintendo",
          "author_url": "https://www.youtube.com/c/nintendo",
          "height": 113,
          "width": 200,
          "version": "1.0",
          "provider_name": "YouTube",
          "provider_url": "https://www.youtube.com/",
          "thumbnail_height": 360,
