      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Pokémon Legends: Arceus",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " is a wonderful proof of concept. It does a lot right and makes a lot of fresh changes to the series and yet, it also has its share of flaws, despite how minor they may be. It’s an exciting time for the series as Game Freak have taken a leap of faith in a game that breaks away from the norms of the series. All in all, ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Pokémon Legends: Arceus",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " takes the series in a fresh direction that I hope Game Freak will stick with as my fear is that this will be a one-time thing. Perhaps they could keep on with the core series, while making a “Legends'' side series.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
